<div className="abPair"><div className="abStart"><div className="box">Immediate Action</div></div><div className="abEnd"><div className="box">When an unarmed fighter successfully <Link to="/rule/trip">trips</Link> an opponent with an unarmed attack, he can attempt a <Link to="/rule/dirty_trick">dirty trick</Link> combat maneuver against that creature (before the opponent becomes prone).</div></div></div>
