<div className="abPair"><div className="abStart"><div className="box">Ability</div></div><div className="abEnd"><div className="box">An unbreakable gains the <Link to="/feat/heroic_defiance">Heroic Defiance</Link> feat as a bonus feat, if he does not have it already. If he already has this feat, the unbreakable can choose any combat feat instead.</div></div></div>
